name: Deepfreeze Continued...
body:
### Welcome to DeepFreeze Continued...
A mod for Kerbal Space Program.    

If you feel like supporting my work go to: [Patreon](https://www.patreon.com/JPLRepo?ty=h)   
If not that's cool too. 
   
You can download the latest release by clicking the links above, or this [link](https://github.com/JPLRepo/DeepFreeze/releases).   
   
The WIKI page is located [here](https://github.com/JPLRepo/DeepFreeze/wiki).   
   
The Forum page is located [here](http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/124720-1-0-4-DeepFreeze-Continued-Bug-Fixes-Enhancements-%28v0-18-2-1%29-11-Sep-2015).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
